      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW QUARK (8) has a strong record here with six wins and three placings from 11 starts. Hit the frame latest (22.12) when second at Warrnambool in a Mix 3/4. Expected to be in the finish. GAS LANTERN (1) hit the ground running from out wide and on speed early but faded and swamped late when 5th at this track in Mix 3/4 company. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Warrants plenty of respect. PAW RIVAL (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 22.30 beating Shima Stripe. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. ASTON WARRIOR (3) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
